description: Works to trees covered by LBE ORDER NO 14 (6) 1975: 3 x Acacia(G1)-reduce crown by up to 1.5m and lift to 5m, 2 x Maple(G2)-reduce crown by up to 2m and lift to 5m, 1x Sycamore(T1)-reduce crown by up to 2.5m and lift to 5m, Mixed species(G4)-reduce height to up to 5ft, 2x poplar(G4)-reduce crown by up to 2m, 1x Ornamental(T3)-reduce and lift crown by up to 1m, Cherry and birch group(G6)-reduce and lift crown by up to 1.5m, 4x Chestnut and 4 x Lime-reduce crown by up to 2.5m and 1x Lime(T2)-fell to ground level.
